| 3H |  ?    | |
|    |  3S   | | natural forcing
|    |  3NT  | | natural, NF
|    | 4C,4D | | natural, F
|    | !4S!  | | #Kickback#
|    | !4NT! | | self-wood ?? +
                 natural 4NT not needed??
|===

[%autowidth,cols="3*^,<",grid="none"]
