| 1S |  2C   | |
| 2H |  3C   | |
| 3H |  ?    | |
|    |  3S   | | natural forcing
|    |  3NT  | | natural, NF
|    | !4S!  | | #Kickback#
|    | 4NT   | | natural
|===

Responder cannot set hearts as trump below game but has a natural and
forcing 3S available.
Therefore, we define 4S as kickback.

=== Picture bids have priority over KC asking

Picture bids are just well defined natural bids, so it's normal for
them to have priority over a KC-asking bid.

